dc_creator_sm: Snohomish County Geographic Information System (GIS), Dept. of Information Services
dc_description_s: Consists of point locations of physical buildings and structures, building complexes, and facilities which serve the public in some capacity.  This includes schools, libraries, fire stations, police stations, churches, hospitals, city halls, post offices, airports, chambers of commerce, museums, and transportation facilities. Also included are (1) Snohomish County  government facilities, (2) current Snohomish County polling places, and (3) 1995 Snohomish County voter registration places.
